SCADA = Supervisory Control and Data Acquisition

Scada permits to control and monitor industrial processes :

-Monitor, gather and process real-time data from anywhere in th world
-Directly interact with devices such as sensors, valves, pumps, motors, and more through human-machine interface (HMI) software
-Control industrial processes and critical infrastructure locally or at remote locations

Scada can be adapt for different enterprises types. It can range from simple configurations to complex installations.
Also use by many modern industries. Energy, food, or our field the manufacturing.

Effective SCADA systems can result in significant savings of time and money. 
